Kate Price (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kate_Price_(actress) 0 Kate Price (born Catherine Duffy, February 13, 1872 – January 4, 1943) was an Irish-born American actress. She is known for playing the role of Mrs. Kelly in the comedy series The Cohens and Kellys, made by Universal Pictures between 1926 and 1932. Price appeared in 296 motion pictures between 1910 and 1937. Kate_Price ( born_Catherine_Duffy , February_13_,_1872 – January_4_,_1943 ) was an_Irish-born_American_actress .
